<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Layout Halaman Muka Website</title>

    <style>

        body{
            margin:0;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background:#fff4f8;
        }

        header{
            background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff7eb3,#ffb6d9);
            color:white;
            padding:18px;
            text-align:center;
        }

        .container{
            width:90%;
            max-width:1000px;
            margin:20px auto;
            background:white;
            border-radius:14px;
            overflow:hidden;
            box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .layout{
            border:2px solid #ffc6dd;
            margin:20px;
        }

        .header-box{
            background:#ffd6e8;
            padding:16px;
            text-align:center;
            font-weight:bold;
            border-bottom:2px solid #ffb6d1;
        }

        .search-box{
            background:#fff0f6;
            padding:14px;
            text-align:center;
            border-bottom:2px solid #ffb6d1;
        }

        .hero-box{
            background:#ffe5f0;
            padding:45px;
            text-align:center;
            border-bottom:2px solid #ffb6d1;
        }

        .hero-box h2{
            margin:0;
            color:#ff4f93;
        }

        .hero-box p{
            margin-top:10px;
            color:#666;
        }

        .content{
            display:flex;
        }

        .main-content{
            width:70%;
            padding:35px;
            border-right:2px solid #ffb6d1;
            background:white;
        }

        .article{
            background:#fff4f8;
            padding:15px;
            border-radius:10px;
            margin-bottom:15px;
        }

        .article h3{
            margin-top:0;
            color:#ff4f93;
        }

        .sidebar{
            width:30%;
            padding:25px;
            background:#fff7fa;
        }

        .sidebar-box{
            background:#ffe5f0;
            padding:15px;
            border-radius:10px;
            margin-bottom:15px;
        }

        .sidebar-box h3{
            margin-top:0;
            color:#ff4f93;
        }

        .footer-box{
            background:#ffd6e8;
            padding:16px;
            text-align:center;
            border-top:2px solid #ffb6d1;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Layout Halaman Muka Website</h1>
</header>

<div class="container">

    <div class="layout">

        <div class="header-box">
            LOGO | Home | About | Login
        </div>

        <div class="search-box">
            Cari artikel atau informasi...
        </div>

        <div class="hero-box">
            <h2>Selamat Datang di Website Kami</h2>
            <p>Website sederhana dengan tampilan layout halaman muka.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">

            <div class="main-content">

                <div class="article">
                    <h3>Artikel Terbaru</h3>
                    <p>Informasi terbaru ditampilkan pada bagian konten utama website.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="article">
                    <h3>Berita Populer</h3>
                    <p>Berisi berita atau informasi yang banyak dilihat pengguna.</p>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="sidebar">

                <div class="sidebar-box">
                    <h3>Kategori</h3>
                    <p>Teknologi</p>
                    <p>Pendidikan</p>
                    <p>Desain</p>
                </div>

                <div class="sidebar-box">
                    <h3>Konten Populer</h3>
                    <p>Layout Website</p>
                    <p>UI dan UX</p>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="footer-box">
            Kontak | Bantuan | Copyright
        </div>

    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
